# Claude Code Context Management
# This file helps Claude focus on relevant code and reduce token usage

# === IGNORE EVERYTHING FIRST ===
*

# === ALWAYS INCLUDE ===
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md

# === CURSOR RULES (for reference) ===
!.cursor/
!.cursor/rules/
!.cursor/rules/manifest.mdc
!Svelte-Component-Library/.cursor/
!Svelte-Component-Library/.cursor/rules/
!Svelte-Component-Library/.cursor/rules/manifest.mdc

# === ALLOW PARENT DIRECTORIES ===
!Svelte-Component-Library/
!client/
!vectorizer/
!backend/

# === SOURCE DIRECTORIES ===
!Svelte-Component-Library/src/
!Svelte-Component-Library/src/**
!client/src/
!client/src/**
!vectorizer/**
!backend/src/
!backend/src/**

# === ALWAYS IGNORE (even in allowed dirs) ===

# Dependencies
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# Build Outputs
**/dist/
**/.svelte-kit/
**/build/
**/.wrangler/
**/.output/
**/.vercel/
**/.netlify/
**/storybook-static/

# Python Virtual Environment
vectorizer/venv/
vectorizer/.venv/
vectorizer/env/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.Python

# Cache & Temporary Files
**/.cache/
**/.vite/
**/.parcel-cache/
**/.turbo/
**/.next/
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.swp
**/*~
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Environment Files (contain secrets)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
backend/.dev.vars

# IDE & Editor Files
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.code-workspace
**/*.sublime-*

# Lock Files (reduce context noise)
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml

# Test & Coverage
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/
**/test-results/

# Misc
**/.history
**/.git.backup/

# === CONTEXT-SWITCHING PATTERNS ===
# Uncomment sections below to focus Claude on specific areas

# Focus on Backend only:
# Svelte-Component-Library/
# client/
# vectorizer/

# Focus on Client only:
# Svelte-Component-Library/
# backend/
# vectorizer/

# Focus on Component Library only:
# client/
# backend/
# vectorizer/

# Focus on Vectorizer only:
# Svelte-Component-Library/
# client/
# backend/
